data.description: This beautiful sought-after ranch home offers a single-story layout with a seamless flow between living spaces.  Walk thru a beautiful 8 ft wooden door into this  gorgeous home and you'll see a very spacious open floor plan. This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath perfectly positioned on 2146 sq. ft. This home sits on a .24 acre lot with a covered patio that overlooks a beautiful wooded area. It also boast 12 ft. ceilings in most rooms with tray ceilings in the Dining and Master Bedroom, coffered ceiling in living room, and cathedral ceilings in Front Bedroom and Master bathroom.  Breathtaking kitchen with quartz countertops, all white cabinets, an oversized island with a stainless appliances.  Stunning brick propane fireplace with a solid wood mantle and shiplap accent wall. Won't last long. Get your buyers in today!!!
